<p>This script installs and configures the applications for you:</p>

<ul>
  <li><a href="https://en.terminalroot.com.br/how-to-install-bspwm-on-gentoo/">bspwm</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://github.com/polybar/polybar">Polybar</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://en.terminalroot.com.br/how-to-install-rofi-in-gentoo-and-create-shortcut-for-it-in-bspwm/">Rofi</a></li>
</ul>

<p>Among other apps with proper settings, like a foss! ðŸ˜ƒ</p>

